content: Learn how to create perfect templates and increase your chance to get approval in our <1>guide</1>.

comment.text: This translation key provides information within a dialog encouraging users to submit forms to a gallery. It explains that a guide exists to help users create high-quality templates and improve their chances of approval. The text appears in the Submit To Form Gallery dialog.
